```
Tile Activation: 5 ns (pre-charged rail)
Active Power: 10 mW (at 1.2 GHz)
Idle Power: 0 mW (0V rail)
Leakage: 2.5 µW (PMIC quiescent)
```

Energy per query (typ): 3.7 µJ (active cycles) + 0 µJ (idle) = 3.7 µJ

